      • changeDetails

        public void changeDetails(java.lang.String oldKey,
                          ContactDetails details)
        Change the details previously stored under the given key.
        Parameters:
        oldKey - One of the keys used to store the details. This should be a key that is currently in use.
        details - The replacement details. Must not be null.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - If either argument is null.
